Interface MeterReadingRepository

All Superinterfaces:
org.springframework.data.repository.CrudRepository<MeterReading,String>, org.springframework.data.repository.ListCrudRepository<MeterReading,String>, org.springframework.data.repository.ListPagingAndSortingRepository<MeterReading,String>, org.springframework.data.mongodb.repository.MongoRepository<MeterReading,String>, org.springframework.data.repository.PagingAndSortingRepository<MeterReading,String>, org.springframework.data.repository.query.QueryByExampleExecutor<MeterReading>, org.springframework.data.repository.Repository<MeterReading,String>
@Repository public interface MeterReadingRepository extends org.springframework.data.mongodb.repository.MongoRepository<MeterReading,String>
Repository interface for MeterReading entities.

Provides CRUD operations and custom query methods for accessing meter readings stored in MongoDB.
